California Pizza Kitchen Execs Hear IMC Presentations</span>
</div>

<div class="blog">


<img src='http://www.medill.northwestern.edu/medill/images/purplewords/inmedillnews.gif' border='0'>

<h3 class='date2'>March 12, 1999</h3>

<div align='right' class="tools">

